data.description: Terrific investment opportunity.  This is a legal 2 family house with at 3 bedrooms and 1 bath on each floor plus living room, kitchen and dining.   Basement is finished with two doors that walk-out to the level yard.   Property sits on a double 50 x 100 lot that is level and can accomodate about 10 cars.   Zoned R6B and offers a great opportunity to build in an area that is seeing record new development.   Within blocks of TWO major hospitals (Montefiore and North Central Bronx) as well as blocks from Metro North Train at Gunhill Road as well as close to the Bronx River Parkway, Botanical Garden, the Bronx Zoo and Fordham University.  Plenty of shops, banks and restaurants in the area.  D train is also just blocks away.  Don't miss out on this rare opportunity.  Property will be sold fully vacant.   Sold as-is.
